{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 32671,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「船と言えば、コパンドンが作らせた奴が",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Speaking of ships, there should be one that Kopandon had made...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32672,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あったはずだが…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"There should have been one...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32673,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あれは今は使えないか。仕方ないな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That one can't be used now, huh? Nothing we can do.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32674,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あれ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32675,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ランス様！　ロッキーさんの足首に、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Lord Rance! Something is wrapped around Rocky-san's ankle.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32676,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　何か巻き付いてますよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " \"Something is wrapped around it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32677,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「む……確かに。飾り紐……か？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm... Indeed. A decorative string... perhaps?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32678,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　海まで繋がってるな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It's connected all the way to the sea.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32679,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ひょいと」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"With a quick flick...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32680,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "すぽーんと、海中に沈んでいたものが",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Something that had been sinking in the sea with a pop"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32681,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "引っ張り上げられた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "was pulled up."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32682,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「便利な奴め…………ん、これは……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"How convenient... Hmm, what is this...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32683,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "砂漠の道を、魔人討伐隊はまっすぐ進む。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The demon-slaying squad moved straight along the desert path."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32684,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ん…………こっち、右に曲がるでち」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm... We take a right here.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32685,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あん？　なんでだ？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh? Why?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32686,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　道も何もないではないか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"There's no path or anything here.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32687,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「道はあるでち。こっちに進まないと、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"There is a path. If you don't go this way,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32688,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どうなるか保証しまちぇんよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I can't guarantee what will happen.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32689,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ランス様……案内人さんの言うことですから……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Lord Rance... we should trust what the guide says...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32690,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ちっ、仕方ない。最短距離で頼むぞ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Tch, it can't be helped. Let's take the shortest route.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32691,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "顎からひっきりなしに流れる汗を拭って、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Wiping the sweat constantly flowing from his chin,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32692,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランスは案内人の後ろに続く。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance followed behind the guide."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32693,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「こんなルートを行き来するのが仕事とはな……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"To think your job is to come and go on a route like this...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32694,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　お前ら、よく生きてるな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You all manage to stay alive well.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32695,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「仕事でちから」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Because it's our job.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32696,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「仕事ってな……もっとマシなモンがあると思うが。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Job, huh... I think there are better things to do.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32697,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それとも全然暑くないのか？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Or are you not hot at all?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32698,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「わたちも別に暑くないわけではありまちぇん。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It's not like I'm not hot either."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32699,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　たまたま、こういうのが向いてたんでち」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I just happen to be suited for this kind of thing.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32700,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………向き不向きってレベルの話か……？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Is it really just a matter of suitability...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32701,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「わたちには、目的があるのでち。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I have a purpose."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32702,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　その為にも、きちんと自活する必要があるのでち」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "For that, I need to live independently.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32703,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「これくらいの暑さなら我慢できまちゅから。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I can endure this kind of heat."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32704,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　他の人にはできない仕事は稼ぎやすいのでち」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The jobs others can't do pay well.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32705,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「け、けっこうしっかりしてるのね……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-you're surprisingly reliable...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32706,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　子供っぽいのに……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even though you're childish...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32707,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「でも、目的って…………？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But, what's your purpose... ?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32708,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………………………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........................\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32709,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「喋りすぎまちたわ。水分が惜しいでち」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I talked too much. Water is precious.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32710,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それきり口を噤んで、日立は黙々と",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "After that, Hitachi fell silent,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32711,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "一行を先導して歩き続けた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and quietly continued leading the group."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32712,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "――――ある日のランス城――",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "----- One day at Rance Castle -----"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32713,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はーにほっ♪　はーにほっ♪」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Honey ho♪ Honey ho♪\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32714,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はにほっ！　はにほっ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Honey ho! Honey ho!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32715,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ハニー達は、今日もランス城を闊歩していた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The Honeys were striding through Rance Castle once again today."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32716,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あのう……すみません。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Um... Excuse me."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32717,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　はにわ避けスプレー、予備あります？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Do you have any backup Haniwa-repellent spray?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32718,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あっ、この間お渡ししたの、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, the one I gave you the other day,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32719,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　もう無くなっちゃいました？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "is already all gone?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32720,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい……なんだか、ハニー臭が強くて……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes... Somehow the Honey smell is too strong...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32721,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「分かりました、ちょっと在庫見てきますね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Understood, I'll go check the stock.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32722,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "厨房――――",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Kitchen -----"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32723,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「お代わりー　お代わりくださいー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Refill! Please give me a refill!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32724,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ハニめし大盛りで、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"A large serving of Honey Rice,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32725,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　よろしくごっちゃんデスッ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "please! Thanks a lot!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32726,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ちょ、ええぇっ、またぁ？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"W-wait, what? Again?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32727,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ハニめしなんて、そんな沢山置いてないわよー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We don't have that much Honey Rice in stock!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32728,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「じゃあパンを食べればいいじゃない！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Then just eat bread!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32729,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「パンでもごっちゃんデスッ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even bread is thanks a lot!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32730,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「くっ……お、おのれーーー！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ugh... Ya, you...!\""
    }
  ]
}

